493
00:34:07,870 --> 00:34:09,830
I don't think I can play with the kids anymore. I'm so tired.

494
00:34:09,830 --> 00:34:12,160
The kids act like that because they're happy to see you after a while.

495
00:34:12,160 --> 00:34:14,800
I know, right?

496
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:19,520
