497
00:34:19,520 --> 00:34:21,870
Director, Ji Su switched his agency.

498
00:34:21,870 --> 00:34:24,410
Oh, I heard. Apparently, it was thanks to your hard work.

499
00:34:24,410 --> 00:34:26,090
He visited?

500
00:34:26,090 --> 00:34:28,620
Wow, he's better than me. I thought he was busy.

501
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:32,360
He just called. And he sent a bunch of snacks for the kids.

502
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:35,950
He takes care of them diligently, calling them his little siblings.

503
00:34:36,710 --> 00:34:39,960
It would take about an hour and a half from here to Gangnam, right?

504
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:42,600
Maybe even three hours for Da Hyeon.

505
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:46,950
Where is it?

506
00:35:48,120 --> 00:35:50,990
You can't find it even when it's right in front of your eyes.

507
00:35:53,830 --> 00:35:55,910
Why the smile?

508
00:35:55,910 --> 00:35:57,930
W-where?

509
00:36:14,460 --> 00:36:17,350
[Family]

510
00:36:26,850 --> 00:36:30,210
Stop looking around. There are no reporters here.

511
00:36:30,210 --> 00:36:33,600
How do you know? There are security cameras everywhere.

512
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:36,710
